Feature: Adding Product to the cart in SnapDeal 

  
  Scenario: Adding product in snapdeal
    Given User must be on the SnapDeal Home Page
    When  Selecting educational toys in the the toys category
    And   Enter your Pincode
    And   Applying filters - offer
    And   Selecting the E Note Pad from that
    And   Add that product to cart
    Then  Product added to the cart
